#how to write a very long string in python using a very short story (vss) written by Lynn Werre

print('''He gathered the remnants of her
favorite vase- the faded floral one that
was chipped in places.
"My vase," she whispered.
"I'll fix it." He was frantic to make it
right. She touched his arm.
"No. Sit with me while I grieve the memories
it held."''')
